# Trivy ignore file
#
# Format: one CVE / misconfig ID per line. Anything after `#` is a
# comment. Document *why* a finding is suppressed so reviewers can
# revisit when the upstream advisory changes.

# AVD-DS-0002: Dockerfile/Dockerfile.dev run as root.
# The worker invokes terraform / packer / openstack CLI against
# bind-mounted git repos. Switching to non-root requires verifying
# that all three toolchains can write into /tmp/worker_repos and
# .terraform plugin caches without permission issues — and that
# bind-mount UIDs line up on macOS + Linux. Tracked in #16.
AVD-DS-0002

